title: Hindi Movie Songs Video.apk
description:
Watch Song Videos from Hindi Movies. All new movie song has been included.
You will able to watch the songs whenever you need to hear!
The song list is updated time to time.
New movies are also added as time passes.
Features:
Inbuilt Video Player.
Video plays both in low and high bandwidth.

Movie songs at present includes:

A Flying Jatt, Akira, Ayaan Mukherjees Next, Azhar, Baaghi, Banjo, Befikre, Cabaret, Dangal, Dishoom, Final Cut Of Director, Great Grand Masti, Happy Bhag Jayegi, Hera Pheri 3, Houseful 3, Housefull 3, Julie 2, Lifes Good, Madaari, Mirzya, Mohenjo Daro, MS Dhoni - The Untold Story, Noor, One Night Stand, Pink, Raabta, Rock On 2, Rustom, San 75 Pachattar, Sarbjit, Shab, Shivaay, The Legend Of Michael Mishra, Tum Bin 2, Veere Di Wedding.

The list will be updated and extended soon!
